  <div class="container mx-auto mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Latest Updates</h2>
    <p>Dear {{consultantName}},</p>
    <p>We are thrilled to have you on board with us. As part of our commitment to supporting your growth and success, we want to keep you informed about the latest updates and developments in the industry.</p>
    <p>Here are some recent trends and news in the {{consultantCategory}} sector:</p>
